result.title: Will Add More Contests Soon!
result.content:
Hey all,

Just wanted to let you know that I've come back to work and have added everyone who wanted to get added to the Codeforces group to it. After several of you do the 2017 Arabella Contest, I'll add another one. Good luck and feel free to email me at my regular email, dmarino@cs.ucf.edu, any time. Thanks!

Arup
